## SEO Metadata (App Router)

Use Next.js App Router `generateMetadata` or `export const metadata` to provide page-level SEO.

### Global (Root Layout)

- Persian defaults set in `metadata` (title template, description, OpenGraph siteName/locale)
- Favicon is served locally from `/favicon.png` in `public`
- Reference: [layout.tsx](mdc:infinity-store-front/src/app/layout.tsx)

### Home (`/`)

- Title: «صفحه اصلی | اینفینیتی استور»
- Description: concise Persian summary of storefront
- Canonical: `/`
- Reference: [home page](<mdc:infinity-store-front/src/app/(product)/page.tsx>)

### PDP (`/pdp/[slug]`)

- Fetch product by slug and build metadata from product attributes
- Title: `خرید {Title} | اینفینیتی استور`
- Description: product `Description` (trim ~160 chars), fallback to Title
- OpenGraph: `type: website`, `url: /pdp/{slug}`, `images` from CoverImage (`IMAGE_BASE_URL + url`)
- Canonical: `/pdp/{slug}`
- Reference: [PDP page](<mdc:infinity-store-front/src/app/(product)/pdp/[slug]/page.tsx>)

### PLP (`/plp`)

- Derive metadata from query context:
  - Search: `نتایج جستجو برای "{q}" | اینفینیتی استور` and canonical `/plp?search={q}`
  - Category: `خرید {category} | اینفینیتی استور` and canonical `/plp?category={category}`
  - Default: `فروشگاه | اینفینیتی استور` and canonical `/plp`
- OpenGraph: `type: website`, `url` aligned to canonical
- Reference: [PLP page](<mdc:infinity-store-front/src/app/(product)/plp/page.tsx>)

### Auth Pages (`/auth/*`)

- Use `export const metadata` with `robots: { index: false, follow: false }`
- Set canonical to the specific route (e.g., `/auth/login`, `/auth/login/otp`, `/auth/forgot-password`, `/auth/forgot-password/verify`, `/auth/register`, `/auth/register/info`)
