### Super Admin (`/super-admin/*`)

- Private/admin section; should not be indexed. Prefer route-group layout `metadata.robots` or per-page metadata as needed
- Reference: [Super Admin layout](<mdc:infinity-store-front/src/app/(super-admin)/layout.tsx>)

### Notes

- Use Persian titles and concise descriptions (~150–160 chars)
- OpenGraph `type` should be one of Next types (e.g., `website`)
- Use `IMAGE_BASE_URL` for absolute image URLs in OpenGraph
- Ensure `alternates.canonical` always matches current route/query context
